thread.title: Chris Scholfield
thread.title_full: Car Mats UK reviewed by Chris Scholfield

author: Chris Scholfield
title: Chris Scholfield
text: The mats arrived very quickly and are of good quality. My only slight criticism is that the mat for the passenger's footwell appears to be slightly too short. Otherwise I'm very happy with the purchase. I'm also pleased that they pick up on the original Audi mounting clips.
